11#include "rtc_base/nat_types.h"
12
13#include "rtc_base/checks.h"
14
15namespace rtc {
16
17class SymmetricNAT : public NAT {
18 public:
19 bool IsSymmetric() override { return true; }
20 bool FiltersIP() override { return true; }
21 bool FiltersPort() override { return true; }
22};
23
24class OpenConeNAT : public NAT {
25 public:
26 bool IsSymmetric() override { return false; }
27 bool FiltersIP() override { return false; }
28 bool FiltersPort() override { return false; }
29};
30
31class AddressRestrictedNAT : public NAT {
32 public:
33 bool IsSymmetric() override { return false; }
34 bool FiltersIP() override { return true; }
35 bool FiltersPort() override { return false; }
36};
37
38class PortRestrictedNAT : public NAT {
39 public:
40 bool IsSymmetric() override { return false; }
41 bool FiltersIP() override { return true; }
42 bool FiltersPort() override { return true; }
43};
44
45NAT* NAT::Create(NATType type) {
46 switch (type) {
47 case NAT_OPEN_CONE:
48 return new OpenConeNAT();
49 case NAT_ADDR_RESTRICTED:
50 return new AddressRestrictedNAT();
51 case NAT_PORT_RESTRICTED:
52 return new PortRestrictedNAT();
53 case NAT_SYMMETRIC:
54 return new SymmetricNAT();
55 default:
56 RTC_NOTREACHED();
57 return 0;
58 }
59}
60
61} // namespace rtc
